# Rauf runtime — transient files that must never be tracked
**/.rauf/.loop.lock
**/.rauf/state.json
**/.rauf/DONE
**/.rauf/CANCEL
**/.rauf/iteration-status.json
**/.rauf/rauf.log
**/.rauf/events.ndjson
**/backlog.json.bak

# Local Claude Code session artifacts
.claude/

# Internal dev planning notes — not part of the public/published surface
plans/

# Adapter build artefacts (forge-agent-adapters-build)
.venv-adapters/
adapters.tmp-*/

# Cross-agent installer (Node package)
installer/node_modules/
installer/dist/
installer/adapters/
installer/LICENSE
**/.rauf/archive/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
